---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Environment and experiences | Agua Sala"
  description="Discover Munigua, the riverbank and the nature near our rural house in Seville."
>
  <section class="container-site py-16 md:py-24">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[--color-brand-700]">Environment</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-4xl text-stone-900 md:text-5xl">Nature, culture and real disconnection</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-stone-600">
      From the house you can enjoy outdoor activities, water spots and routes with their own personality. Very close is Munigua, a Roman site of great value.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr]">
      <img
        src="/images/munigua-1.png"
        alt="Archaeological remains of Munigua with brick arches"
        class="h-[360px] w-full rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-md ring-1 ring-stone-200"
      />
      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[--color-brand-700]">Featured</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900">Munigua, living history in the midst of nature</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
          Munigua was an ancient Roman city located in a unique mining and natural environment.
          Today it preserves archaeological remains of great interest, such as thermal structures and the high sanctuary, which offer a different visit for those seeking culture and landscape in the same getaway.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <img
        src="/images/munigua-2.png"
        alt="View of the Munigua sanctuary on the hillside"
        class="h-[250px] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/paisaje-1.png"
        alt="Panoramic view of the surroundings of Villanueva del Rio y Minas"
        class="h-[250px] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Munigua</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
          An essential visit for lovers of history, heritage and cultural hiking.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Riverbank and landscape</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
          Quiet paths, open views and areas to enjoy with family.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Near Seville</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
          Combine rural serenity with urban outings in the same trip.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>